#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cantor; is an application to allow you to you use your favorite "
"mathematical applications from within an elegant &kde;-integrated Worksheet "
"Interface. It provides dialogs to assist with common tasks and allows you to "
"share your worksheets with others."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; je aplikacija, ki vam omogoča uporabo vaših najljubših matematičnih "
"aplikacij znotraj elegantnega vmesnika za delovne liste, integriranega v "
"&kde;. Zagotavlja pogovorna okna za pomoč pri pogostih opravilih in omogoča "
"skupno rabo delovnih listov z drugimi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &cantor;"
msgstr "Uporaba &cantor;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot:"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &cantor;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &cantor;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "&cantor; features"
msgstr "&cantor; lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Intuitive worksheet view for evaluating expressions."
msgstr "Intuitivni pogled delovnega lista za vrednotenje izrazov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results of graph plotting shown inside the worksheet."
msgstr "Rezultati risanja grafov, prikazani znotraj delovnega lista."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Easy plugin-based structure to allow different backends to be added."
msgstr ""
"Preprosta struktura, ki temelji na vtičnikih in omogoča dodajanje različnih "
"ozadij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GetHotNewStuff integration to allow example worksheets to be downloaded (or "
"uploaded)."
msgstr ""
"Integracija GetHotNewStuff, ki omogoča prenos (ali nalaganje) primerov "
"delovnih listov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mathematical formula typesetting using &latex;."
msgstr "Stavljenje matematične formule z uporabo &latex;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backend-aware syntax highlighting."
msgstr "Označevanje sintakse, ki upošteva zaledje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plugin-based assistant dialogs to help with common tasks, such as "
"integrating a function, or entering a matrix."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorna okna pomočnika na osnovi vtičnikov za pomoč pri pogostih "
"opravilih, kot je integracija funkcije ali vnos matrike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &cantor; backends"
msgstr "&cantor; zaledja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cantor; offers you several choices for the backends you wish to use with "
"it. The choice to make depends on what you want to achieve."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; vam ponuja več možnosti za zaledja, ki jih želite uporabiti z njim. "
"Izbira je odvisna od tega, kaj želite doseči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currently the following backends are available:"
msgstr "Trenutno so na voljo naslednja zaledja:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sage:"
msgstr "Sage:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sage is a free open-source mathematics software system licensed under the "
"GPL. It combines the power of many existing open-source packages, within a "
"common Python-based interface. See <ulink url=\"https://sagemath.org"
"\">https://sagemath.org</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Sage je prosti odprtokodni matematični programski sistem z licenco GPL. "
"Združuje moč številnih obstoječih odprtokodnih paketov znotraj skupnega "
"vmesnika, ki temelji na Pythonu. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url="
"\"https://sagemath.org\">https://sagemath.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maxima:"
msgstr "Maxima:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maxima is a system for the manipulation of symbolic and numeric expressions, "
"including differentiation, integration, Taylor series, Laplace transforms, "
"ordinary differential equations, systems of linear equations, polynomials, "
"sets, lists, vectors, matrices, and tensors. Maxima yields high-precision "
"numeric results by using exact fractions, arbitrary precision integers, and "
"variable precision floating point numbers. Maxima can plot functions and "
"data in two and three dimensions. See <ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge."
"net\">http://maxima.sourceforge.net</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Maxima je sistem za manipulacijo simbolnih in numeričnih izrazov, vključno z "
"diferenciacijo, integracijo, Taylorjevo vrsto, Laplaceovo transformacijo, "
"navadnimi diferencialnimi enačbami, sistemi linearnih enačb, polinomi, "
"množicami, seznami, vektorji, matricami in tenzorji. Maxima daje visoko "
"natančne numerične rezultate z uporabo natančnih ulomkov, poljubno natančnih "
"celih števil in števil s plavajočo vejico s spremenljivo natančnostjo. "
"Maxima lahko izriše funkcije in podatke v dveh in treh dimenzijah. Za več "
"informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge.net\">http://maxima."
"sourceforge.net</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>R:</term>"
msgstr "<term>R:</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"R is a language and environment for statistical computing and graphics, "
"similar to the S language and environment. It provides a wide variety of "
"statistical (linear and nonlinear modelling, classical statistical tests, "
"time-series analysis, classification, clustering, data science, ...) and "
"graphical techniques, and is highly extensible. The S language is often the "
"vehicle of choice for research in statistical methodology, and R provides an "
"open-source route to this. See <ulink url=\"https://www.r-project.org"
"\">https://www.r-project.org</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"R je jezik in okolje za statistično računalništvo in grafiko, podobno jeziku "
"in okolju S. Omogoča široko paleto statističnih (linearno in nelinearno "
"modeliranje, klasični statistični testi, analiza časovnih vrst, "
"klasifikacija, združevanje v skupine, ...) in grafičnih tehnik ter je zelo "
"razširljiv. Jezik S je pogosto izbrano sredstvo za raziskave v statistični "
"metodologiji, R pa ponuja odprtokodno pot do tega. Za več informacij glejte "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.r-project.org\">https://www.r-project.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Julia:"
msgstr "Julia:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Julia is a high-level, high-performance, general-purpose dynamic programming "
"language for technical computing, with syntax that is familiar to users of "
"other technical computing environments. It provides a sophisticated "
"compiler, distributed parallel execution, numerical accuracy, and an "
"extensive mathematical function library. See <ulink url=\"https://julialang."
"org/\">Julia website</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Julia je visoko-nivojski, visoko-zmogljiv jezik za splošno-namensko "
"dinamično programiranje za tehnično računalništvo s sintakso, ki je "
"uporabnikom znana iz drugih tehničnih računalniških okolij. Zagotavlja "
"prefinjen prevajalnik, porazdeljeno vzporedno izvajanje, numerično "
"natančnost in obsežno knjižnica matematičnih funkcij. Glejte <ulink url="
"\"https://julialang.org/\">spletno mesto Julia</ulink> za več informacij."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra;:"
msgstr "&kalgebra;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalgebra; is a MathML-based graph calculator, that ships with &kde; "
"Education project. See <ulink url=\"https://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/\">https://"
"edu.kde.org/kalgebra/</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"&kalgebra; je grafični kalkulator, ki temelji na MathML in je priložen "
"Izobraževalnemu  projektu  &kde;. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url="
"\"https://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/\">https://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Qalculate!:"
msgstr "Qalculate!:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Qalculate! is not your regular software replication of the cheapest "
"available calculator. Qalculate! aims to make full use of the superior "
"interface, power and flexibility of modern computers. The center of "
"attention in Qalculate! is the expression entry. Instead of entering each "
"number in a mathematical expression separately, you can directly write the "
"whole expression and later modify it. The interpretation of expressions is "
"flexible and fault tolerant, and if you nevertheless do something wrong, "
"Qalculate! will tell you so. Not fully solvable expressions are however not "
"errors. Qalculate! will simplify as far as it can and answer with an "
"expression. In addition to numbers and arithmetic operators, an expression "
"may contain any combination of variables, units, and functions. See <ulink "
"url=\"https://qalculate.github.io/\">https://qalculate.github.io/</ulink> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Qalculate! ni vaša redna programska replikacija najcenejšega razpoložljivega "
"kalkulatorja. Qalculate! želi v celoti izkoristiti vrhunski vmesnik, moč in "
"prilagodljivost sodobnih računalnikov. V središču pozornosti v Qalculate! je "
"vnos izraza. Namesto da bi vsako število v matematični izraz vnesli posebej, "
"lahko neposredno napišete celoten izraz in ga pozneje spremenite. Razlaga "
"izrazov je prilagodljiva in tolerantna na napake, in če kljub temu naredite "
"kaj narobe, Qalculate! bo to takoj povedal. Nerešljivi izrazi pa niso "
"napake. Qalculate! bo poenostavil, kolikor lahko, in odgovoril z izrazom. "
"Poleg števil in aritmetičnih operatorjev lahko izraz vsebuje poljubno "
"kombinacijo spremenljivk, enot in funkcij. Za več informacij glejte <ulink "
"url=\"https://qalculate.github.io/\">https://qalculate.github.io/</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Python2 and Python3:"
msgstr "Python2 in Python3:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Python is a remarkably powerful dynamic programming language that is used in "
"a wide variety of application domains. There are several Python packages to "
"scientific programming."
msgstr ""
"Python je izjemno zmogljiv dinamični programski jezik, ki se uporablja v "
"najrazličnejših aplikacijskih domenah. Obstaja več paketov Python za "
"znanstveno programiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Python is distributed under Python Software Foundation license (GPL "
"compatible). See the <ulink url=\"https://www.python.org/\">official "
"website</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Python se distribuira pod licenco Python Software Foundation (združljivo z "
"GPL). Za več informacij obiščite <ulink url=\"https://www.python.org/"
"\">uradno spletno stran</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This backend adds an additional item to the &cantor;'s main menu, "
"<guimenu>Package</guimenu>. The only item of this menu is "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Package</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import Package</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This item can be used to import Python packages "
"to the worksheet."
msgstr ""
"To zaledje doda dodaten element v glavni meni &cantor;, <guimenu>Paket</"
"guimenu>. Edini element v tem meniju je <menuchoice><guimenu>Paket</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi paket</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta element "
"lahko uporabite za uvoz paketov Python na delovni list."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scilab:"
msgstr "Scilab:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scilab is an free software, cross-platform numerical computational package "
"and a high-level, numerically oriented programming language."
msgstr ""
"Scilab je prosta programska oprema, večplatformni numerični računski paket "
"in visokonivojski numerično usmerjen programski jezik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scilab is distributed under CeCILL license (GPL compatible). See <ulink url="
"\"https://www.scilab.org/\">https://www.scilab.org/</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Scilab se distribuira pod licenco CeCILL (združljivo z GPL). Za več "
"informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://www.scilab.org/\">https://www.scilab."
"org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need Scilab version 5.5 or higher to be installed in your system to make "
"this backend usable."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo tega ozadja morate v sistem namestiti Scilab različice 5.5 ali "
"novejšo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Octave:"
msgstr "Octave:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU; Octave is a high-level language, primarily intended for numerical "
"computations. It provides a convenient command line interface for solving "
"linear and nonlinear problems numerically, and for performing other "
"numerical experiments using a language that is mostly compatible with <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.mathworks.com/products/matlab.html\">MATLAB</ulink>. See "
"<ulink url=\"https://octave.org/\">https://octave.org/</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"&GNU; Octave je jezik visoke ravni, namenjen predvsem numeričnim izračunom. "
"Zagotavlja priročen vmesnik ukazne vrstice za numerično reševanje linearnih "
"in nelinearnih problemov ter za izvajanje drugih numeričnih poskusov z "
"uporabo jezika, ki je večinoma združljiv z <ulink url=\"https://www."
"mathworks.com/products/matlab.html\" >MATLAB</ulink>. Za več informacij "
"glejte <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/octave/\"></ulink> za več "
"informacij."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lua:"
msgstr "Lua:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lua is a fast and lightweight scripting language, with a simple procedural "
"syntax. There are several libraries in Lua aimed at math and science."
msgstr ""
"Lua je hiter in lahek skriptni jezik s preprosto proceduralno sintakso. V "
"Lui je več knjižnic, namenjenih matematiki in naravoslovju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <ulink url=\"https://www.lua.org/\">https://www.lua.org/</ulink> for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://www.lua.org/\">https://www.lua."
"org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This backend supports <ulink url=\"https://luajit.org/\">LuaJIT 2</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To zaledje podpira <ulink url=\"https://luajit.org/\">LuaJIT 2</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &cantor; Workspace"
msgstr "&cantor; Delovni prostor"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; Workspace</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; Delovni prostor</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; Workspace</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; Delovni prostor</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Worksheet interface of &cantor; consists of three parts:"
msgstr "Vmesnik delovnega lista &cantor; sestavljajo trije deli:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tab bar, where you can switch through the open worksheets."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica z zavihki, kjer lahko preklapljate med odprtimi delovnimi listi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A help panel, where help for a specific command is displayed if you enter "
"<userinput>?? <replaceable>command</replaceable></userinput>, "
"<userinput>describe(<replaceable>command</replaceable>)</userinput> or "
"<userinput>example(<replaceable>command</replaceable>)</userinput> "
"(<application>Maxima</application> backend)."
msgstr ""
"Plošča s pomočjo, kjer se prikaže pomoč za določen ukaz, če vnesete "
"<userinput>?? <replaceable>ukaz</replaceable></userinput>, "
"<userinput>describe(<replaceable>ukaz</replaceable>)</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>example(<replaceable>ukaz</replaceable>)</userinput> "
"(<application>Maxima</application> backend)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Variable Manager panel where you can see the list of all available "
"variables on the current worksheet. The Help and Variable Manager panels are "
"shown as tabs on a sidebar of a &cantor; window. Variable manager can be "
"used for Maxima (if enabled on <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &cantor;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"<guilabel>Maxima</guilabel> page), &kalgebra;, Octave, Python2, Python3, "
"Qalculate, and Scilab backends only."
msgstr ""
"Plošča Upravljalnik spremenljivk, kjer si lahko ogledate seznam vseh "
"razpoložljivihspremenljivke na trenutnem delovnem listu. Plošči Pomoč in "
"Upravitelj spremenljivk staprikazani kot zavihki na stranski vrstici okna "
"&cantor;. Upravitelj spremenljivk se lahkouporablja se za Maxima (če je "
"omogočeno v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &cantor;... samo za</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>stran <guilabel>Maxima</guilabel>), &kalgebra;, Octave, Python2, "
"Python3, zaledja Qalculate in Scilab."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "The worksheet itself."
msgstr "Sam delovni list."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Worksheet"
msgstr "Delovni list"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The worksheet is the basic area for working with &cantor;. Using it, you can "
"enter expressions, allow the backend to perform calculations, and look at "
"the results. The commands the worksheets accept depend on the chosen "
"backend, so you should learn the appropriate backend syntax (the "
"<guibutton>Show Help</guibutton> button takes you there directly). If you "
"know the command, but you need additional information, you can type \"? "
"<replaceable>command</replaceable>\", and contextual help will appear on the "
"right of the worksheet. If you want to see some example worksheets, you can "
"go to <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Download Example "
"Worksheets</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, and download worksheets "
"other users have published."
msgstr ""
"Delovni list je osnovno področje za delo s &cantor;. Z njegovo uporabo "
"lahkovnesete izraze, dovolite zaledju, da izvede izračune in pogledate "
"rezultate. Ukazi, ki jih sprejmejo delovni listi, so odvisni od izbranega "
"zaledja, zato bi se morali naučiti ustrezne sintakse zaledja (Gumb "
"<guibutton>Pokaži pomoč</guibutton> vas popelje neposredno tja). Če poznate "
"ukaz, vendar potrebujete dodatne informacije, lahko vnesete \"?"
"<replaceable>command</replaceable>«, in kontekstualna pomoč se bo pojavila "
"nadesno od delovnega lista. Če želite videti nekaj primerov delovnih listov, "
"lahkopojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Primer "
"prenosaDelovni listi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> element menija in prenesite "
"delovne listeso objavili drugi uporabniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To control each command entry of the worksheet you can use control buttons "
"shown at the right part of the worksheet when hovering the entry field with "
"a mouse cursor. There are three basic actions for each entry: "
"<guilabel>Evaluate Entry</guilabel> to update the result of calculations for "
"the entry, <guilabel>Drag Entry</guilabel> to move the entry at the other "
"place of the current worksheet and <guilabel>Remove Entry</guilabel> to "
"remove the entry from the current worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Za nadzor vsakega ukaznega vnosa na delovnem listu lahko uporabite nadzorne "
"gumbeprikazane na desnem delu delovnega lista, ko se pomaknete na vnosno "
"polje s kazalcem miške. Za vsak vnos obstajajo tri osnovna dejanja: "
"<guilabel>Ovrednoti vnos</guilabel> za posodobitev rezultata izračunov za "
"vnos, <guilabel>povlecite vnos</guilabel>, da premaknete vnos na drugo mesto "
"trenutnega delovnega lista in <guilabel>Odstrani vnos</guilabel> v "
"odstranite vnos s trenutnega delovnega lista."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Font settings and alignment of worksheet entries can be changed using a "
"toolbar above the worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve pisave in poravnavo vnosov na delovnem listu lahko spremenite z "
"uporabo aorodne vrstice nad delovnim listom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu allows you to change some settings of "
"the appearance of your current worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> vam omogoča spreminjanje nekaterih "
"nastavitev videza vašega trenutnega delovnega lista."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Typeset using LaTeX"
msgstr "Nastavitev z uporabo LaTeXa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting changes the way results are presented to you. If enabled, it "
"passes the result through the &latex; system, to produce visually appealing "
"formulas. For example, <quote>3*x^2*sqrt(2)*x+2/3</quote> becomes"
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev spremeni način prikaza rezultatov. Če je omogočeno, posreduje "
"rezultat skozi &latex; sistem za ustvarjanje vizualno privlačnih formul. Na "
"primer <quote>3*x^2*sqrt(2)*x+2/3</quote> postane"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "3*x^2*sqrt(2)*x+2/3"
msgstr "3*x^2*sqrt(2)*x+2/3"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax Highlighting"
msgstr "Označevanje sintakse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Syntax Highlighting increases the readability of code, by highlighting "
"keywords, or matching brackets in different colors."
msgstr ""
"Označevanje sintakse poveča berljivost kode z označevanjem ključnih besed "
"ali ujemanjem oklepajev v različnih barvah."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completion"
msgstr "Dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, &cantor; will show you possible completions for the "
"command you are currently typing when you press the Tab-key. If there is "
"only one choice remaining, it will insert the rest of the command for you."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, vam bo car pokazal možne zaključke za ukaz, ki ga "
"trenutno vnašate, ko pritisnete tabulatorsko tipko. Če obstaja ostane le še "
"ena izbira, bo namesto vas vstavil preostali del ukaza."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Numbers"
msgstr "Številke vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether the different expressions should have a number "
"in front. This allows you to recall older results - in Maxima, for instance, "
"this is done with the <quote>%O1</quote> command."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzira, ali naj imajo različni izrazi številko spredaj. To "
"vam omogoča, da prikličete starejše rezultate - v Maximi, na primer, to "
"storite z ukazom <quote>%O1</quote>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Animate Worksheet"
msgstr "Animirajte delovni list"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether the different animations will be used to "
"highlight changes on a worksheet."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzira, ali bodo različne animacije uporabljene za "
"označevanje sprememb na delovnem listu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Embedded Math"
msgstr "Vdelana matematika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether rendering math expressions inside <literal>$$.."
"$$</literal> in Text and &Markdown; entries is enabled by default (needs "
"<application>pdflatex</application> installed)."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzira, ali upodabljanje matematičnih izrazov znotraj "
"<literal>$$..$$</literal> v besedilu in &Markdown; vnosi so privzeto "
"omogočeni (potrebuje nameščen <application>pdflatex</application>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "The assistant dialogs"
msgstr "Pomočnikova pogovorna okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several assistant dialogs implemented in &cantor; to alleviate "
"some basic operations."
msgstr ""
"V &cantor; je implementiranih več pogovornih oken pomočnika. za olajšanje "
"nekaterih osnovnih operacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These dialogs can be accessed using the main menu items. Each backend has "
"its own assistant dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Do teh pogovornih oken lahko dostopate z elementi glavnega menija. Vsako "
"zaledje ima lastna pogovorna okna pomočnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Create Matrix dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Ustvari matriko"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; matrix creation dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za ustvarjanje matrice</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; matrix creation dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za ustvarjanje matrice</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog can be used to input matrices. You can define matrix dimensions "
"and its elements."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno lahko uporabite za vnos matrik. Določite lahko dimenzije "
"matrike in njenih elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to navigate between cells quickly during input using the "
"&Tab; key."
msgstr "Med vnosom je mogoče hitro krmariti med celicami s tipko &Tab;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matrix operation dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za delovanje matrice"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; matrix input dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za vnos matrike</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; matrix input dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za vnos matrice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering name of the matrix to compute its eigenvectors, "
"eigenvalues or invert matrix. The default value (<userinput>%</userinput>) "
"is used to refer to the previous result of calculation or input."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos imena matrike za izračun njenih lastnih "
"vektorjev, lastnih vrednosti ali inverzne matrike. Privzeta vrednost "
"(<userinput>%</userinput>) se uporablja za sklicevanje na prejšnji rezultat "
"izračuna ali vnosa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Differentiation dialog"
msgstr "Diferenciacijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; differentiation dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za razlikovanje</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; differentiation dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno razlikovanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering expression of the function to differentiate, the "
"name of the variable and the order of derivative."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos izraza funkcije za razlikovanje, imena "
"spremenljivke in vrstnega reda izpeljave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration dialog"
msgstr "Integracijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; integration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; integracijsko pogovorno okno</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; integration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; integracijsko pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering expression of the function to integrate, the "
"name of the variable and the limits of integration (for the definite "
"integral)."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos izraza funkcije za integracijo, imena "
"spremenljivke in limitov integracije (za določen integral)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Solve equations dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za reševanje enačb"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; solve equation dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za reševanje enačbe</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; solve equation dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za rešitev enačbe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering equations to solve (each equation in a separate "
"line) and the variables to determine (separated by the comma)."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos enačb za reševanje (vsaka enačba v ločeni "
"vrstici) in spremenljivk za določitev (ločenih z vejico)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Package import dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za uvoz paketa"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; package import dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za uvoz paketa</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; package import dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za uvoz paketa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering name of the package to import (&eg; "
"<userinput>numpy</userinput> for Python)."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos imena paketa za uvoz (&eg; <userinput>numpy</"
"userinput> za Python)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plot dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za izris"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot dialog (Functions tab)</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za izris (zavihek "
"Funkcije)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot dialog (Functions tab)</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za izris (zavihek "
"Funkcije)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options of this dialog are separated into two groups using tabs. The "
"<guilabel>Functions</guilabel> tab allows entering functions to plot."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti tega pogovornega okna so z zavihki ločene v dve skupini. Zavihek "
"<guilabel>Funkcije</guilabel> omogoča vnos funkcij za izris."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter new function click on the <guibutton>Add</guibutton>. Double-click "
"on the <guilabel>Title</guilabel> cell and enter the title, then double-"
"click on the <guilabel>Expression</guilabel> cell and enter the function "
"expression."
msgstr ""
"Za vnos nove funkcije kliknite <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Dvokliknite "
"celico <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel> in vnesite naslov, nato dvokliknite "
"celico <guilabel>Izraz</guilabel> in vnesite funkcijski izraz."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot dialog (Options tab)</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za izris (zavihek "
"Možnosti)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot dialog (Options tab)</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno za izris (zavihek "
"Možnosti)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Options</guilabel> tab is used to define plot and legend "
"options. You can fine-tune almost every plot option to obtain the pleasant "
"look of your figure."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> se uporablja za določanje možnosti "
"izrisa in legende. Skoraj vsako možnost risbe lahko natančno prilagodite, da "
"dobite prijeten videz svoje slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plot 2D dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za risanje 2D"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot 2D dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; izriši pogovorno okno 2D</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot 2D dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; izris pogovornega okna 2D</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering expression of the function, its variable and the "
"limits for this variable."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos izraza funkcije, njene spremenljivke in "
"omejitev za to spremenljivko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plot 3D dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za risanje 3D"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot 3D dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno risanja 3D</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of the &cantor; plot 3D dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &cantor; pogovorno okno risanja 3D</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog allows entering expression of the function, its variables and "
"the limits for each variable."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno omogoča vnos izraza funkcije, njenih spremenljivk in "
"omejitev za vsako spremenljivko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &cantor; window"
msgstr "Glavni &cantor; okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cantor; has the common &kde; menu items, for more information read the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the "
"&kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; ima skupno &kde; elementov menija, za več informacij preberite "
"poglavje <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; "
"Osnove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is the list of the additional or special menu items in &cantor;. "
"Please note that some menus are only shown for backends that have "
"corresponding implementation."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je seznam dodatnih ali posebnih elementov menija v &cantor;. "
"Upoštevajte, da so nekateri meniji prikazani samo za ozadja, ki imajo "
"ustrezno izvedbo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new worksheet with the default backend."
msgstr "Ustvari nov delovni list s privzetim zaledjem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Backend</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Zaledje</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new worksheet with the chosen backend."
msgstr "Ustvari nov delovni list z izbranim zaledjem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a supported new worksheet with the file dialog."
msgstr "Odpri podprt nov delovni list s pogovornim oknom datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri nedavno</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose a worksheet from a list of recently used files."
msgstr "Izberi delovni list s seznama nedavno uporabljenih datotek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Download Example Worksheets</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prenos primerov delovnih listov</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the dialog to download examples uploaded by other &cantor; users with "
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:MyLanguage/"
"Glossary#Get_Hot_New_Stuff\">GetHotNewStuff</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno za prenos primerov, ki so jih naložili drugi &cantor; "
"uporabniki z <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:MyLanguage/"
"Glossary#Get_Hot_New_Stuff\">GetHotNewStuff</ulink>."

