"Namestil sem Sage/Maxima ali drug podprt CAS, vendar se ustrezno zaledje ne "
"prikaže."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One possible explanation is that &cantor; did not correctly detect the "
"location. Go to the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &cantor;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog "
"and change the <guilabel>Path</guilabel> to the appropriate application on "
"the backend's page."
msgstr ""
"Ena možna razlaga je, da &cantor; ni pravilno zaznal lokacije. Pojdite v "
"pogovorno okno <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &cantor;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"spremenite <guilabel>Pot</guilabel> v ustrezno aplikacijo v zaledju strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "What a peculiar name - what does it have to do with mathematics?"
msgstr "Kako nenavadno ime - kaj ima opraviti z matematiko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cantor; is named after the German mathematician <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Cantor\">Georg Cantor</ulink>, the creator of set "
"theory."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; je poimenovan po nemškem matematiku <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Cantor\">Georgu Cantorju</ulink>, ustvarjalcu "
"teorije množic."

